 a growing skills gap, leaders must find innovative ways to stay competitive and drive excellence. This session will dive into how AI can streamline project management by enhancing workflows, optimizing resources and improving decision-making.<\/p>\n<p>Attendees will discover practical applications of AI for improving project management processes, from automating routine tasks to providing advanced insights for strategic planning. We will address common barriers to AI adoption and offer a strategic framework for effectively integrating these technologies into your business operations. By the end of this session, participants will understand how to leverage AI to increase efficiency, elevate project delivery, and gain a competitive edge in the evolving industry landscape.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Join this session to:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Understand how AI can enhance project management processes, including automation, resource optimization, and workflow improvements.<\/li>\n<li>Learn practical strategies for overcoming barriers to AI adoption and developing a framework for integrating AI technologies into your firm\u2019s operations.<\/li>\n<li>Gain insights into how AI can support strategic decision-making and boost project delivery and profitability, positioning your firm for success in a competitive industry.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<!-- \/wp:fl-builder\/layout -->","pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"729ff674","settings":{"editor":"<p class=\"fl-heading\">Speaker<\/p>","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":30,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"700","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"30","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","__globals__":{"text_color":"globals\/colors?id=primary"}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"1480a70d","settings":{"editor":"<h2 class=\"fl-heading\">Bret Tushaus<\/h2>","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"7b2da5da","settings":{"editor":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Bret-HEadshot.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-32349\" title=\"Bret Tushaus\" src=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Bret-HEadshot.jpg\" alt=\"Deltek\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" \/><\/a>Bret Tushaus is an architect by education and a seasoned professional in the architecture, engineering, construction, and consulting industries. After being a loyal Deltek customer for 15 years, Bret joined Deltek\u2019s product management team in 2010 and currently holds the position of Vice President of Product Management.<\/p>\n<p>In his role, Bret manages a diverse portfolio of Deltek products, primarily focusing on delivering ERP and other technology solutions tailored to address operational pain points for organizations in the industry. With a strong emphasis on project management, Bret is dedicated to amplifying its importance and leveraging technology and digital transformation to support project managers and refine project management disciplines.<\/p>\n<p>As a thought leader and trusted advisor, Bret plays a crucial role in shaping the future of project management solutions at Deltek, ensuring that organizations have the necessary tools for successful project outcomes. His expertise and passion for delivering value-driven solutions have established him as an influential figure in the field.<\/p>","_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"1d07ef0c","settings":{"editor":"<p>Facilitator<\/p>","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":30,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"700","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","__globals__":{"text_color":"globals\/colors?id=primary"}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"4f7bd08e","settings":{"editor":"<h2 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Fiona Johann, PMP, AEC PM | Engineering Management Institute<\/h2>","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"539700f2","settings":{"editor":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Fiona-Headshot-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-75695\" title=\"Fiona Johann, PMP, AEC PM\" src=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Fiona-Headshot-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>With years of experience in higher education honing leadership skills among faculty, Fiona Johann now partners with AEC engineers to help them become outstanding project managers and leaders. Drawing on her PMP certification and extensive background in leadership development, she equips professionals with the tools and strategies needed to excel in project delivery and team management.<\/p>","_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"100","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"}],"settings":{"template":"elementor_canvas"},"metadata":{"_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes":"3","_yoast_wpseo_content_score":"60","be_title_toggle_hide":"1","disable_sitewide_popup":"a:1:{i:0;s:4:\"true\";}","_yoast_wpseo_wordproof_timestamp":"","_yoast_wpseo_meta-robots-noindex":"1","_yoast_wpseo_meta-robots-nofollow":"1"}}